 someone who works for a computer company about a problem that you have had with your computer. Read the email and write your reply.</instructions><email>Dear Mr Llewellyn, #We received your phone message about a problem with your printer. #We tried to call you back but there was no answer. #Can you explain the problem to us? #We will get back to you as soon as possible. #Regards, #O Braithwaite (Manager, Vixen Computers Ltd)</email><item><choice correct="1">Dear Mr Braithwaite, </choice><choice>To O Braithwaite,</choice><choice>Hello, Mr Braithwaite,</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">Thank you for your email.</choice><choice>Thanks for everything.</choice><choice>Thanks for fixing my computer. </choice></item><item><choice correct="1">My printer isn't working.</choice><choice>My printer has run out.</choice><choice>My printer is breaking.</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">I checked to see if the paper had run out</choice><choice>I checked the engineers</choice><choice>I checked to see the printer</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">and I tried turning it off,</choice><choice>and I tried to see the matter,</choice><choice>and I tried my printer,</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">but it's still out of order.</choice><choice>but I'm still out of order.</choice><choice>but it can't go.</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">I need my computer for my work.</choice><choice>I am needing my computer for my work.</choice><choice>My computer needs me.</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">Please call me as soon as possible.</choice><choice>Call me as soon possible.</choice><choice>Please fix it.</choice></item><item><choice correct="1">Regards, John Llewellyn</choice><choice>See you soon, John Llewellyn</choice><choice>Your sincerely, John</choice></item></activity></DOC>